categories: Category:Imperial Intelligence personnel of the Galactic Empire

nodes.text: Tal Burren was a grade-four tech of Imperial Intelligence as of 4 ABY. His superior was Ivak.

A dark-skinned Human male, he made the jump from grade-four all the way to the hitherto nonexistent grade-thirteen by helping Ysanne Isard override Mara Jade's tampering with the Imperial Palace's computer system.
